Package api

Class NodeData

java.lang.Object
api.NodeData
All Implemented Interfaces:
node_data, java.io.Serializable
public class NodeData
extends java.lang.Object
implements node_data, java.io.Serializable
This class implements a node_data interface that represents the set of operations applicable on a node (vertex) in a directional weighted graph. The vertex's neighbors and the connected edges are implemented by HashMap for high efficiency.
